channel.description: i need help...im in the middle of switching my server form hamachi to no-ip i have no-ip and i opened port, but for port forwarding what do i make name and port? i know my ip...i know to check enable and UDP and TCP, but what name do i save as and what port do i do? if anyone could help me that would be great :] ps: i hope this is right section if not, please don't yell at me and no dick head posters calling me a noob cuz i don't know what to do!

item.title: Por forwarding, what do i save
item.dc:creator: @n0va_k0 n0va k0
item.description:
@n0va_k0 wrote:

On your default gateway site, put name as anything you want. Start and end port as 43594 and 43594. Check the little box, protocol as both.That’s about it, Haven’t had to portforward again in a long time, so if I am missing anything tell me
